{"tid":352661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔止勒索老師、影子學生 興德學校涉偽造聘請文件","createTime":"2017-08-09T02:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T07:22:49.000Z","uid":19552,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1e8230f9ec7d06c794d4024bcff44987f38acb9","tid":352661,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:42:20.000Z","msg":"被指行政和管理不善的屯門興德學校，除涉以「影子學生」方法騙取教育局更多津貼外，更被爆出懷疑偽造文件。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，屯門警署於6月23日接獲一名32歲姓李男子報案，指屯門慶平路一學校懷疑有人使用虛假文書。警方同時接獲有關轉介，並展開調查。案件暫列「行使虛假文書」，交屯門警區重案組第一隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。 <br />\n<br />\n廉署發言人則表示，根據政策，廉署一般不會評論個別事件，在接獲貪污投訴後，如有足夠資料，廉署必定會依法跟進。<br />\n<br />\n興德校長陳章萍在記者會被問到有否偽造文件時，陳反問「點解我要偽造文件」，指聘請人手時有同事會處理招聘信件，亦會安排人手接見應徵者，另又有校內書記確認合約等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/753750/xlarge/d590684902bd33ee753ad5b9561be7dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F753750%2Fxlarge%2Fd590684902bd33ee753ad5b9561be7dd.jpg&h=4dff6529&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40b57e9fcea2c9d173d536be57492ef7a06cf191","tid":352661,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:46:35.000Z","msg":"肥婆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等入倉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606d92494d0a2f6acc7e4f759ba95ff13a8b2d93","tid":352661,"uid":17081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:49:28.000Z","msg":"單人倉會唔會唔夠位住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a48385010c967222d38388c9270bc09e95cfd3","tid":352661,"uid":5419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:50:25.000Z","msg":"拉尻個肥婆入冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7994e947386c2558e835c5911e5b7301111b65","tid":352661,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:50:39.000Z","msg":"